# JVM Performance Tuning Configuration
# These flags optimize GC behavior and heap management for high-throughput transaction processing

# Modern low-latency garbage collector (G1GC)
-XX:+UseG1GC
-XX:MaxGCPauseMillis=200
-XX:G1HeapRegionSize=16m

# Heap sizing (2GB min, 4GB max)
# Adjust based on available system memory
-Xms2g
-Xmx4g

# String deduplication to reduce memory footprint
-XX:+UseStringDeduplication

# Performance optimizations
-XX:+DisableExplicitGC
-XX:+AlwaysPreTouch
-server
